The paper proposes a novel algorithm for optimizing radial basis function (RBF) networks, which are a type of neural network. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also mentions that the algorithm can be applied to control systems (cs.SY) and information theory (cs.IT), but these are less likely sub-categories.
